- Drag Characters to form word

- "Merge visible layers" to combine them
	- left click on layer pane

- Create White border
	- Filters ---> Light and Shadow ---> Drop Shadow
	- Manage Presets ----> Navigate to CreateLogosWithGimp/GIMP_presets/Drop_Shadow
	- 1-LogoWhite will create border
	- 2-LogoColor will add primary color to border

- Add Another Drop Shadow
	- Filters ----> Light and Shadow ----> Drop Shadow
